### A.8 Agent Messages

```rust
enum AgentMessage {
    Request    { origin_task: TaskId, hops: u8, body: Bytes },
    Response   { origin_task: TaskId, hops: u8, body: Bytes },
    Delegation { origin_task: TaskId, hops: u8, body: Bytes },
    Result     { origin_task: TaskId, hops: u8, body: Bytes },
